    "The category includes data produced directly by SMBs (first-party data) and data collected by third-party entities (external assessments).",
    "Social Media & Investor Forums.",
    "This includes content from public platforms where individual investors discuss financial markets.",
    "Social media posts are real-time and high-volume, often opinionated and informal (emojis, memes, humor, or hyperbole).",
    "Annotation often relies on crowd-sourcing of sentiment and toxicity labels."
